{"tid":1457713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由聽日起 所有散水撚都係鬼！去留由前線決定","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:46:04.000Z","uid":222581,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c804aa8fbd4c5987e893dcf593008b0d85a5c5d0","tid":1457713,"uid":222581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"我明有啲散水撚係擔心前線先係咁叫人走<br />\n但你有無諗過你咁樣會害咗前線？<br />\n六月開始已經講緊走唔走前線決定<br />\n不嬲都係越少人越危險 <br />\n就算開真槍 多啲人至少有能力反抗<br />\n你叫啲人走把撚？啲人嚟緊支援都畀你屌走埋<br />\n本身今日贏撚硬 我嚟到一半都畀你地fake走埋<br />\n由聽日起 前線去留前線決定<br />\n邊個叫走邊個就係鬼 見一個block一個<br />\n<br />\n今日做咗散水撚嘅唔緊要 聽日補救<br />\n明天機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afb2424f8791a53de20af7a810713fd3cc34d13","tid":1457713,"uid":37753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"唔再需要討論散唔散水狗"},{"pid":"b82b078e85582bfc8039775e519a109e4080565e","tid":1457713,"uid":209781,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"真 叫人走個啲一定係屋企做冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"f4121d1e16fe9203dbddd3d5fe751b6bbca5fc82","tid":1457713,"uid":284804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣標籤對運動真係冇好處 我都有屌人散水 但係我唔肯定係將來叫人散水嘅人合唔合理"},{"pid":"0df13abe820099a356d47ef7c78b06e1d637b7c9","tid":1457713,"uid":282134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"我散水唔係驚<br />\n係覺得個今日咁做效率好高<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔洗俾人拉<br />\n又可以令佢取消班機</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只係用左幾個鐘</span></span><br />\n日日咁做唔好？"},{"pid":"6d9994434b821ebf934ada66f8bffdd4e90672a7","tid":1457713,"uid":284804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"起碼今日真係抵屌先"},{"pid":"96f63bb9b687fb8054ab8d61ba33894cf170f88b","tid":1457713,"uid":282134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df13